ngineer known for his exceptional work in the music industry. Mak Blaze’s contribution to “Tolani” adds a level of quality that is sure to impress. Furthermore, “Tolani” is dedicated to Sarmyfire’s late friend Rico Swavey. Through this track, Sarmyfire honors his friend’s memory and pays tribute to the support and impact he had on his life and career. In addition to the single, Sarmyfire is currently working on a full-length project that he plans to release later this year. Fans can expect more innovative sounds and collaborations as he pushes boundaries and showcases his talents.
Listen here to Tolani. 